flowchart TD
    A["Pulse from\nFlow Sensor N"] --> B[ISR Triggered]
    B --> C[Read millis]
    C --> D{"Millis - lastPulseTime > 5ms?"}
    D -->|Yes valid pulse| E["Increment pulseCount[N]"]
    D -->|No bounce| F[Ignore]
    E --> G["Update lastPulseTime[N]"]
    G --> H["Return to Main Loop"]
    F --> H